  m_text: "<size=20><b>Universal Water System 2</b>\r</size>\r\n\n<size=16><b>Sea
    Rendering Features:</b></size>\r\n- Real-time FFT Wave Calculation\r\n- 3-layer
    Waves\r\n- LOD Mesh for Infinite Water\n- PBR Shading\r\n- Reflection\r\n- Refraction\r\n-
    Subsurface Scattering\r\n- Caustics\n\r\n<size=16><b>Interactive Elements:</b></size>\r\n-
    Buoyancy\r\n- Ship Dynamics\r\n- Wake Foams\r\n\r"
